{"tid":1425191,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實各位仲想犧牲幾多義士","createTime":"2019-08-06T17:23:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T18:37:35.000Z","uid":2448,"like":47,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"784d24419aa2fdec5b6eeefaee76b4fc96e98a5e","tid":1425191,"uid":2448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:23:53.000Z","msg":"每次既行動 就係SET防線 等狗放TG 之後趁亂拉人<br />\n跟住返到屋企屌狗 搵律師救義士 但其實仲有無用?<br />\n次次都話義士一個都不能少 但佢地比人拉個陣 有無做過D咩<br />\n我地每次都有住人數上既優勢 你話真係唔小心落單比畜龍拉到都算<br />\n但防暴推個陣 都有拉過人架啵 點解唔可以防暴拉人個陣 我地推返佢地去救人呀 <br />\n佢地救人個陣 一定有所分心 我地仲要人多 係咪一定救唔到呢<br />\n我明白佢地每次推個陣都放TG係好難頂 但和理非們可唔可以都唔好跑得咁快 就算勇武想救人都有BACKUP <br />\n希望大家唔好再淨係得把口<br />\n 手足真係一個都不能少"},{"pid":"1a758ef0549abad7e38f01121feed4f91a6e728e","tid":1425191,"uid":2448,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:26:27.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4c1f3fd4ac92fae2c7571606bccdde383323cbd6","tid":1425191,"uid":2448,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:27:58.000Z","msg":"勇武只會越拉越少架咋"},{"pid":"a0f45c29dd7c5abfdc896accb9fd4c00c8e95cf3","tid":1425191,"uid":57797,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:28:38.000Z","msg":"聽撚到厭"},{"pid":"ab05cc14a74084ca96fadb42d0ee5ad935d96575","tid":1425191,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:29:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f609438d9884e0e6e0860570febb307731ecd365","tid":1425191,"uid":2448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a0f45c29dd7c5abfdc896accb9fd4c00c8e95cf3","tid":1425191,"uid":57797,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:28:38.000Z","msg":"聽撚到厭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:29:28.000Z","msg":"但比人拉既係越黎越多"},{"pid":"5a358c825fbcd1451edff12bc6dc7687f4f8b27f","tid":1425191,"uid":142002,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:30:13.000Z","msg":"呢句真，我開始有啲厭倦tg放題<br />\n我支持勇武，但會唔會有better way?"},{"pid":"9baf2465bde93b8f84892032f34a87ae0ba1752f","tid":14